# PyMatrix - Personal Digital Rain Animation

A fun and creative digital rain animation for your terminal.

## 📦 Installation
```bash
pip install pymatrix
```

## 🎮 Basic Usage
```bash
pymatrix
```

For full documentation, visit [pymatrix.vercel.app](https://pymatrix.vercel.app).
